## Speech recognition model

**NVIDIA Parakeet-TDT 0.6B v3**
- Upstream: https://huggingface.co/nvidia/parakeet-tdt-0.6b-v3
- ONNX conversion used here: https://huggingface.co/istupakov/parakeet-tdt-0.6b-v3-onnx
- License: CC-BY-4.0
- Attribution: Transcription powered by NVIDIA's Parakeet-TDT 0.6B v3 model,
