When redistributing this project in a form that includes or implies use of the
model, preserve this attribution per CC-BY-4.0 §3(a).

## Rust dependencies

See `Cargo.toml` and `Cargo.lock` for the full dependency tree. All direct
dependencies are under permissive licenses (MIT, Apache-2.0, or both). Run
`cargo license` or `cargo about` for a full audit if publishing.

Notable dependencies:
- transcribe-rs (MIT) — model inference wrapper
- ort (MIT/Apache-2.0) — ONNX Runtime Rust bindings
- tokio (MIT) — async runtime
- evdev (Apache-2.0) — /dev/input event reading
